First Department,

December, 1977

(December 1, 1977) In the Matter of the Estate of Saul Brown, Deceased. Joyce Brown, Appellant; Evelyn B. Parker et al., Coexecutors, Respondents.

Decree, Surrogate’s Court, New York County, entered on December 28, 1976, unanimously affirmed on the opinion of the Special Referee, without costs and without disbursements. Concur—Kupferman, J. P., Lupiano, Birns and Silverman, JJ.
